<plot>Emily wakes up one morning only to discover that her world has been turned upside-down. Quite literally actually, as she wakes up on the ceiling of her apartment! Just when things seem like they couldn't get any worse, down-to-earth Simon arrives to take Emily on a date; a date she has completely forgotten about. Now they're not only trying to figure out this bizarre, existential problem, but are really testing the theory that opposites do indeed attract.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?633237</url></doc>
